						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of sheep for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mahādēva at Tiruchchōṟṟuttuṟai with an <hi rend="italic">uḻakku</hi> of ghee every day by a shepherd of the place named Kiḻavaṉ Tattaṉ, who left the gift in charge of an other local shepherd.</p>						

